{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"leetcode","postPath":"lc-paint-fence","post":{"title":"栅栏涂色","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_思路一\">思路一</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_思路二\">思路二</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/paint-fence/\">276. 栅栏涂色</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这一题之前做过，现在看又看不懂了，这里记一下思路备查。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_思路一\">思路一</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>记前 <code>t</code> 个栅栏有 <code>dp[t]</code> 种涂法。现在的问题是，已知 <code>dp[0]</code> 到 <code>dp[t-1]</code>，由此推出 <code>dp[t]</code>。这样，最后的答案就是 <code>dp[n]</code>。\n<code>dp[t]</code> 有两种方式得到：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li>\n<p>第 <code>t</code> 个栅栏和第 <code>t-1</code> 个的颜色不同，这时共有 <code>dp[t-1] * (k-1)</code> 种涂法；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>第 <code>t</code> 个占了和第 <code>t-1</code> 个的颜色相同，这要求第 <code>t-1</code> 个栅栏和第 <code>t-2</code> 个的颜色不同，共 <code>dp[t-2] * (k-1)</code> 种涂法。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>故 <code>dp[t] = dp[t-1] * (k-1) + dp[t-2] * (k-1)</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">n</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">k</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> numWays = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">n, k</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (n == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dp = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, k, k * k]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) {\n        dp[i] = dp[i<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>] * (k<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>) + dp[i<span class=\"hljs-number\">-2</span>] * (k<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>);\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> dp[n];\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这段代码因为只使用了 <code>dp</code> 数组的最后两项来递推，所以只要保存最后两项，就可以把 <code>dp</code> 数组省掉了。改动代码如下：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">n</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">k</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> numWays = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">n, k</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (n == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (n == <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> k;\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dp = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, k, k * k]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dpi_2 = k, dpi_1 = k * k\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> dpi = dpi_1 * (k<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>) + dpi_2 * (k<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>);\n        dpi_2 = dpi_1;\n        dpi_1 = dpi;\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> dpi_1;\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>另外，因为这个递推公式中，<code>k</code> 是常数，所以可以求出 <code>dp</code> 数组的通项公式。见 TODO:</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_思路二\">思路二</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>记录两个 <code>dp</code> 数组，<code>dp1[t]</code> 表示第 <code>t</code> 个栅栏和第 <code>t-1</code> 个颜色相同的涂法数量，<code>dp2[t]</code> 表示第 <code>t</code>\n个栅栏和第 <code>t-1</code> 个颜色不同的涂法数量。于是有下面的关系：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li>\n<p><code>dp1[t] = dp2[t-1]</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>dp2[t] = (dp1[t-1] + dp2[t-1]) * (k - 1)</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>最后的答案就是 <code>dp1[n] + dp2[n]</code>。因为这俩 <code>dp</code> 数组我们只用最后一项，所一干脆就记录最后一一项，从而把数组给省了。\n代码如下：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">n</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">k</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> numWays = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">n, k</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (n == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dp1 = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 表示和前一个相同的数量</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dp2 = k; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 表示和前一个不同的数量</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) {\n        [dp1, dp2] = [dp2, (dp1 + dp2) * (k - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)];\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> dp1 + dp2;\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"LeetCode","toc":[{"title":"53. 最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-subarray"},{"title":"62. 不同路径","path":"lc-unique-paths"},{"title":"70. 爬楼梯","path":"lc-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"121. 买卖股票","path":"lc-buy-stock"},{"title":"132. 分割回文串 II","path":"lc-palindrome-partitioning-ii"},{"title":"198. 打家劫舍","path":"lc-house-robber"},{"title":"276. 栅栏涂色","path":"lc-paint-fence"},{"title":"303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变","path":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable"},{"title":"746. 使用最小花费爬楼梯","path":"lc-min-cost-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"146. LRU 缓存机制","path":"lc-lru-cache"},{"title":"数完全二叉树节点","path":"lc-count-complete-tree-nodes"}],"path":"leetcode"}},"__N_SSG":true}